pl_remarks: data for 2011 after mortality designated by 99999 in DBH column, sapwood depth calculated with published relationship (see Schafer et al 2014, 10.1002/hyp.10104) and sapwood area (see Renniger et al 2015, 10.3389/fpls.2015.00297). LAI is estimated via littertraps and then allocated to each tree according to sapwood area. Bark thickness did not have a relationship with diameter and assumed roughtly the same throughout . For pine see Carlo et al 2016, 10.1093/treephys/tpw044
